// Übersicht aller Landing Pages
---
<html lang="de">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow" />
  <title>Fit on Time, Landing Pages</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/images/logo.png" />
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif; background: #0b0b0f; color: #f0eff2; min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
    .wrap { max-width: 600px; width: 100%; padding: 40px 20px; }
    h1 { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; text-align: center; }
    .sub { font-size: 14px; color: #888; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 32px; }
    .lps { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; }
    a { display: block; background: #151519; border: 1px solid #1c1c22; border-radius: 12px; padding: 16px 20px; color: #f0eff2; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s; }
    a:hover { border-color: #2b7de9; background: #1c1c22; }
    a strong { display: block; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    a span { font-size: 13px; color: #888; }
    .badge { display: inline-block; background: rgba(74,222,128,0.12); color: #4ade80; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 10px; margin-left: 8px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <h1>Fit on Time LPs</h1>
    <p class="sub">Alle aktiven Landing Pages</p>
    <div class="lps">
      <a href="/schilddruesen-report/"><strong>Schilddrüsen-Report <span class="badge">LIVE</span></strong><span>Quiz-Funnel: Schilddrüsen-Check → Report → Booking</span></a>
      <a href="/blockaden-report/"><strong>Blockaden Report <span class="badge">NEU</span></strong><span>Ayurveda Körpertyp-Quiz (Vata/Pitta/Kapha) → Ergebnis</span></a>
      <a href="/stoffwechsel-report/"><strong>Stoffwechsel Report <span class="badge">NEU</span></strong><span>Stoffwechsel-Report mit 7 Fragen + Tipps → Report</span></a>
      <a href="/stoffwechsel-test/"><strong>Stoffwechsel Test <span class="badge">NEU</span></strong><span>Stoffwechsel-Profil mit 7 Fragen → Ergebnis</span></a>
      <a href="/abnehmpotential/"><strong>Abnehmpotential <span class="badge">NEU</span></strong><span>Abnehmpotential-Quiz → Blockade-Analyse</span></a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
